sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Mobile
  participant Backend
  participant AI
  participant Admin
  User->>Mobile: Register
  Mobile->>Backend: Account details
  Backend-->>Mobile: Tokens + OTP challenges
  User->>Mobile: Submit OTP/email code
  Mobile->>Backend: Verify phone/email
  User->>Mobile: Upload media
  Mobile->>Backend: Register media URL
  Backend->>AI: Analyze image
  AI-->>Backend: Trust score + flags
  User->>Mobile: Capture selfie and ID
  Mobile->>Backend: Submit verification
  Backend->>AI: Liveness, OCR, face match
  AI-->>Backend: Verification score
  Backend->>Admin: Queue suspicious items
  Admin->>Backend: Review decision
  Backend-->>Mobile: Matching eligible

